==Description==
Valentin is just one of the many inhabitants on the [[Island of the Francos]], who is searching for the lost [[Franco Key Fragment]]. Unlike many of the others who are searching for the fragment, Valentin uses common sense, knowledge and a metal detector to try and find it.

==Role in Twinsen's adventure==
Valentin gave [[Twinsen]] a clue, that the fragment might be buried near the gas.

